          href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/author-dita.html"
          format="html" scope="external"/>.</p>
      <p>We have a list of videos, some of them DITA-related here: <xref
          href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/videos.html" format="html" scope="external"/> and a series
